      ],
      "tagged_at": "2025-07-10T14:45:06.432549"
    },
    {
      "chunk_text": "We'll come back to that later.Now more about Tarana BurkeYes, Tarana worked with marginalized women in neglected American communities, shocking numbers of whom were victims of sexual violence and abuse.Here she is talking with the BBC World Service's program Hard Talk about how the MeToo movement continues to speak up for voiceless women and girls.",
      "chunk_id": "e46604f3-b83d-469e-92ee-49e04fa5d2db",
      "chunk_index": 3,
      "episode_id": "6865015b66c1a4e8d1176705",
      "original_filename": "RSS_262026947_podcast_1304_What difference has MeToo made_.json",
      "collection_name": "RSS_262026947",
      "chunk_length": 350,
      "enhanced_tags": [
        "ES"
      ],
      "tagged_at": "2025-07-10T14:45:06.435044"
    },
    {
      "chunk_text": "Tarana doesn't call the girls and women who were abused victims.Instead, she prefers the term survivors, people who are able to carry on with their life successfully despite very unpleasant experiences.",
      "chunk_id": "4a00ef7b-cd41-4730-9c7a-59df0db73f75",
      "chunk_index": 4,
      "episode_id": "6865015b66c1a4e8d1176705",
      "original_filename": "RSS_262026947_podcast_1304_What difference has MeToo made_.json",
      "collection_name": "RSS_262026947",
      "chunk_length": 202,
      "enhanced_tags": [
        "XP",
        "ES"
      ],
      "tagged_at": "2025-07-10T14:45:06.437348"
    },
    {
      "chunk_text": "The MeToo movement went viral when several famous movie actresses came forward, offered to give information about sexual harassment.While these Hollywood actresses were famous celebrities, most survivors of sexual violence are ordinary women living ordinary lives.That's why Tarana calls the MeToo movement a unifier, something that unites and brings people together, in this case women of different race and social background.",
      "chunk_id": "e125c927-3f05-46c7-818f-dd3cb141cbe8",
      "chunk_index": 5,
      "episode_id": "6865015b66c1a4e8d1176705",
      "original_filename": "RSS_262026947_podcast_1304_What difference has MeToo made_.json",
      "collection_name": "RSS_262026947",
      "chunk_length": 427,
      "enhanced_tags": [
        "BRI",
        "CI",
        "ES"
      ],
      "tagged_at": "2025-07-10T14:45:06.439915"
    },
    {
      "chunk_text": "But while the media focused on particular people, Weinstein and several actresses in the movie industry, Tarana is clear that the problem is bigger than just individual cases.Here she is explaining about the wider reasons behind the MeToo movement.",
      "chunk_id": "f07d4bd0-1f5d-4a2f-a430-ed7dafd0cfde",
      "chunk_index": 6,
      "episode_id": "6865015b66c1a4e8d1176705",
      "original_filename": "RSS_262026947_podcast_1304_What difference has MeToo made_.json",
      "collection_name": "RSS_262026947",
      "chunk_length": 248,
      "enhanced_tags": [
        "BI",
        "XP",
        "ES",
        "AI"
      ],
      "tagged_at": "2025-07-10T14:45:06.442262"
    },
    {
      "chunk_text": "Tarana says that the behavior of abusers like Weinstein was not challenged or questioned because of their privilege.",
      "chunk_id": "57d024c8-3703-471c-8b58-b0da02be6f16",
      "chunk_index": 7,
      "episode_id": "6865015b66c1a4e8d1176705",
      "original_filename": "RSS_262026947_podcast_1304_What difference has MeToo made_.json",
      "collection_name": "RSS_262026947",
      "chunk_length": 116,
      "enhanced_tags": [
        "ES"
      ],
      "tagged_at": "2025-07-10T14:45:06.444442"
    },
    {
      "chunk_text": "Power and advantage held by a small group of people, usually because of their high social position or because they are rich.So rather than focusing on individual cases, it's male-dominated social structures like privilege that need dismantling, breaking up or being stopped from working by gradually reducing its power over a period of time.Tarana knows the problem won't disappear overnight.But she believes the MeToo movement has overcome",
      "chunk_id": "6a5422bd-7f62-4a05-a13f-f6ba61c96be6",
      "chunk_index": 8,
      "episode_id": "6865015b66c1a4e8d1176705",
      "original_filename": "RSS_262026947_podcast_1304_What difference has MeToo made_.json",
      "collection_name": "RSS_262026947",
      "chunk_length": 440,
      "enhanced_tags": [
        "CI",
        "ES"
      ],
      "tagged_at": "2025-07-10T14:45:06.447045"
    },
    {
      "chunk_text": "and opened up a space to talk about sexual",
      "chunk_id": "58f4a756-fbee-4ff8-8b96-529f5f7cf1b6",
      "chunk_index": 9,
      "episode_id": "6865015b66c1a4e8d1176705",
      "original_filename": "RSS_262026947_podcast_1304_What difference has MeToo made_.json",
      "collection_name": "RSS_262026947",
      "chunk_length": 42,
      "enhanced_tags": [
        "SPA"
      ],
      "tagged_at": "2025-07-10T14:45:06.449130"
    },
    {
      "chunk_text": "harassment in Hollywood.And these actresses were supported",
      "chunk_id": "4ce9d119-7eae-4938-8807-246a02fe3fcc",
      "chunk_index": 10,
      "episode_id": "6865015b66c1a4e8d1176705",
      "original_filename": "RSS_262026947_podcast_1304_What difference has MeToo made_.json",
